Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:08:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Nakashima Yuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:10:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the voice of Hinomori Shiho from Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,for this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so excited that Leo/need's long-awaited first one-man live as pros is finally happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter says, "Personally, I would love to see an MC segment where everyone swaps instruments during the actual show."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I would definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,like to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But she might hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in her position, I would be incredibly nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shiho had to play the drums or the keyboard instead of the bass,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she would actually be willing to go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They did it because it was just a rehearsal, but when it comes to music,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,she is so confident in her skills that her pride might make her refuse even for an MC segment, but I still want to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her getting all flustered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to see everyone struggling and saying they can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I could listen to that and watch it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am looking forward to seeing how the story develops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really imagine Shiho on the drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems like she would be good at keeping rhythm, so she might handle it well, but
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,since your hands and feet have to move differently, she might end up fumbling after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to see her on guitar too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She would definitely end up saying she can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely want to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please look forward to the future story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have picked out another scene that I personally want to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's take a look right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The one I chose is from Episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you play the guitar as well as the bass, Nakashima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She is giving up on both the one-man and the Fan Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.96,0:18:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she looked into everything she possibly could on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She understands how both sides of the audience feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about Hona-chan's role as a leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She still hasn't found
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the answer within herself as to which is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is great that she researches every little detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to show the way. Ichika-chan told her not to take it all on herself, and it is something for everyone to decide, but if she stays indecisive, it might just lead everyone astray.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,she needs to make up her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is wonderful that she feels she has to decide on her own feelings here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But I also hope it doesn't become too much of a burden for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The fans will definitely be happy with a new song for the one-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And she thinks Saki-chan and Shiho-chan would surely want to do that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 7 was great too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes you feel like you aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants people who love Virtual Singers to hear their music too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika-chan surely feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think too much, you won't be able to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have to choose one,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What I choose is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.32,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I need to report urgently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The timing was so perfect, it really surprised me.
Comment: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the request for the new song for the Fan Festa has been withdrawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't due to any fault on our part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The representative just contacted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they heard back from the creator who was ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you mean the person who was originally in charge of the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:21:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they'll be able to finish all three songs as planned, and they were very apologetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.04,0:21:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded like they were ready to prostrate themselves over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad they're feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a bit disappointing that the offer fell through, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we actually received a new request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A new one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The rep said they'd love to have Leo/need perform in the 'Freshman Slot' at the next Fan Festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's partly to make up for this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit further out, but I think we should consider it positively.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's in the future, there shouldn't be any scheduling issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to the rest of the members about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no rush, so feel free to take your time deciding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry for causing so much confusion in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm glad we found out before we officially accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.08,0:22:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best to support you so you can focus on the one-man live and the new songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll leave contacting the other members to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get in touch with the staff for the one-man live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to proceed with the setlist that includes the new song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.53,0:23:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so relieved right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.20,0:23:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had to make a choice, that I had to pick one over the other, but now that I don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.32,0:23:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:23:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.04,0:23:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I happened to avoid it, but there will surely be times in the future when I have to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.48,0:24:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Times when I'll have to make a decision where there is no right answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.84,0:24:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to become someone who can make those choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.09,0:24:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.73,0:24:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So that I can lead everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's leading herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.20,0:24:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As the leader of Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.79,0:24:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.17,0:24:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.83,0:24:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was Episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.12,0:24:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, the scene that caught my attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:25:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The part that left an impression was when Honami-chan said she would definitely choose...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.00,0:25:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She seemed a bit down, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.78,0:25:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The scene where she resolves to lead everyone as their leader was really moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.28,0:25:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me, I'd probably be more optimistic, like 'Oh, wow!'
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.88,0:25:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I'd feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.88,0:25:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had a job like being a leader before, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.68,0:25:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.78,0:25:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it?
Comment: 0,0:25:36.24,0:25:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.24,0:25:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I find her strong sense of responsibility to be quite reliable,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.26,0:25:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but I also don't want her to take things too heavily. If she keeps going like that, she might break,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.92,0:25:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so it was a scene that made me worry about Honami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.70,0:25:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I chose this scene for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, the offer was almost withdrawn, but then they were told they could have a slot...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.02,0:26:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You might feel lucky, but if it was withdrawn without a second chance, you'd definitely regret not speaking up sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.48,0:26:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Decisions like that are really difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.34,0:26:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are many times in life when you have to make those kinds of choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.16,0:26:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how Honami will make her choices from now on, or
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.44,0:26:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of path Leo/need will take, but
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.50,0:26:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep watching over them. I hope they don't end up on bad terms or
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.94,0:26:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,have their mental health suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.52,0:26:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly don't know what kind of story is waiting for us either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.04,0:26:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.36,0:26:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.08,0:27:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Project Sekai event stories always leave some kind of foreshadowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.08,0:27:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural, since the story continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.84,0:27:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's natural, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish she could share some of Yukki's lightheartedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.04,0:27:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it's still too early for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.44,0:27:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still high school students, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.92,0:27:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to worry a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.84,0:27:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and learn from their failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.92,0:27:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.29,0:27:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, there was one more scene that caught my eye personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.64,0:27:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in Episode 7, and it also appeared in the middle of Episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.82,0:27:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I really liked the part in Episode 7 where Honami and Ichika go to see Miku's concert. Ichika was more excited than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.88,0:27:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She was all giddy,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.00,0:27:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,like, "It's Miku!"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.80,0:27:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.08,0:28:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about featuring that part too, but
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.40,0:28:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,if I did, I'd just end up saying "how cute" the whole time, just like the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.64,0:28:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to stick with Episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.88,0:28:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 7 was really cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.68,0:28:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me want to watch it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.12,0:28:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.84,0:28:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go back and read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.26,0:28:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That part was truly adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.12,0:28:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to a Miku concert too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.56,0:28:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.47,0:28:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.56,0:28:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when the title was still "MikuPa," I'm from Wakayama,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.48,0:28:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was a concert there. I was just as excited as Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, "It's Miku!"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.54,0:28:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's Miku!"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.82,0:28:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was getting all hyped up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.55,0:28:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.14,0:28:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everyone to experience that feeling too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.30,0:28:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I got a bit sidetracked again. This time,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.64,0:28:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a look at the card illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.80,0:29:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll share some comments from the illustration team regarding the outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.86,0:29:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This story was about Honami realizing the importance and weight of making decisions as a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.02,0:29:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an episode about a leader's struggles, but the design reflects a positive outlook on the best choice for Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.24,0:29:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspired by the rhythmic song, it captures a lightheartedness that keeps moving forward, with a sweet cuteness rare for the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.00,0:29:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The design features pop and cute star patterns along with casual sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.72,0:29:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,To show them choosing their path, each of the three has a planisphere-like element in their outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.06,0:29:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We also incorporated items where the color palette is meant to resemble a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.40,0:29:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This palette represents the choice between Leo/need's new song and Miku's song,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.40,0:29:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,symbolizing the many choices that will continue to appear in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.64,0:30:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.56,0:30:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where should we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.56,0:30:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.44,0:30:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we usually start with the 4-stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.48,0:30:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the 4-stars then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.72,0:30:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.70,0:30:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the card illustration for the scene that appeared in Episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.36,0:30:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the pre-training version.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.24,0:30:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Honami has a bit of a surprised look on her face, but that smartphone case is so soothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.84,0:30:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a Shiba Inu on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.28,0:30:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like one. It's very comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.00,0:30:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the post-training version.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.44,0:30:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.12,0:30:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is in portrait orientation. It looks even better when you view it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.36,0:30:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Leo/need hasn't really had anything this pop and cute until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.54,0:30:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.80,0:30:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.00,0:31:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much detail in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.84,0:31:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And look, there's a dog in the building in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.24,0:31:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it. There's a compass on the bag too.
Comment: 0,0:31:09.80,0:31:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.80,0:31:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.92,0:31:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is Honami's post-training art.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.08,0:31:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And the can is actually apple juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.32,0:31:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.96,0:31:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.44,0:31:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.24,0:31:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika's training art.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.60,0:31:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This was in Episode 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.96,0:31:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika was telling us not to worry too much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.71,0:31:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.34,0:31:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is the post-training version.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.36,0:31:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.00,0:31:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm losing my vocabulary here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.14,0:31:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.68,0:31:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say anything but 'it's good.' I love how the whole scene is visible in Ichika's art.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.16,0:32:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way she's sitting with her knees up with her guitar on her back is just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.88,0:32:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it 'sankaku-zuwari' (triangle sit).
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.22,0:32:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it's called?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.45,0:32:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.68,0:32:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my regional dialect is showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.16,0:32:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is 'sankaku-zuwari' a Kansai thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.97,0:32:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,People say it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.20,0:32:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never heard it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.30,0:32:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.54,0:32:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.88,0:32:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.62,0:32:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.20,0:32:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.80,0:32:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I meant 'taiiku-zuwari' (gym sit).
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.39,0:32:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.87,0:32:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.92,0:32:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a dialect?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.08,0:32:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.92,0:32:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't sitting like that feel so 'student-like'?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.44,0:32:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't really sit like that once you're an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.36,0:32:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe only during a photoshoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.08,0:32:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If they tell you to sit there like a student, you might do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.48,0:32:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being told 'taiiku-zuwari' is standard, but 'sankaku-zuwari' is Kansai-only.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.42,0:32:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.32,0:32:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.72,0:32:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I personally love it because it feels so much like a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.36,0:33:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the background... there are so many instruments!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.25,0:33:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.28,0:33:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,there are so many, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.72,0:33:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guitar, a bass, an acoustic guitar...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.56,0:33:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can even see some drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.62,0:33:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.54,0:33:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.35,0:33:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.60,0:33:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.28,0:33:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pre-training Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.36,0:33:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all excited for a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.60,0:33:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.42,0:33:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leo/need Rin is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.26,0:33:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love how she's overflowing with that 'gyaru' vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.72,0:33:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.98,0:33:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And that paper chain around her neck... she definitely made that herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.60,0:33:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a student would.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.58,0:33:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When you have a party, you always put those up on the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.44,0:33:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.84,0:33:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And are those loose socks?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.84,0:33:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's another great touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.40,0:33:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It really adds to the gyaru feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.96,0:33:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.64,0:34:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the post-training art.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.14,0:34:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.64,0:34:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.50,0:34:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This really captures all of Rin's...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.76,0:34:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I love that she's wearing a sleeveless top underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.32,0:34:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you call this part...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.70,0:34:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.12,0:34:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I love that she's walking along the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.12,0:34:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so like Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.16,0:34:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell her not to swing her instrument around.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.80,0:34:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell her not to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.16,0:34:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Loose socks really are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.64,0:34:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Trends always come back around eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.44,0:34:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.64,0:34:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And that ribbon is just adorable too.
Comment: 0,0:34:44.48,0:34:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.48,0:34:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It suits her so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.43,0:34:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.08,0:34:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That sigh... she's just too cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.64,0:34:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for Shiho...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.80,0:34:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiho's Training card.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.20,0:34:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for this, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.08,0:35:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for drawing such a lovely illustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.96,0:35:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.54,0:35:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I could just spin around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.84,0:35:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.61,0:35:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.32,0:35:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the YouTube comments and seeing myself spin on the lag,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.12,0:35:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.60,0:35:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.84,0:35:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.96,0:35:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.24,0:35:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks drowsy. Maybe she slept too much the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.84,0:35:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks so sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.88,0:35:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.00,0:35:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Very much so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.64,0:35:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, on the wall in the back, is that a photo
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.20,0:35:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,from the autumn shuffle event? Having that there is a nice touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.80,0:35:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I should look at this instead of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.80,0:35:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.04,0:35:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy I can see the details of Shiho's room like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.58,0:35:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and even the soles of her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.04,0:36:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, they're wearing shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,or you just can't see their feet at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.92,0:36:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing the soles of a character's feet, especially a 2D one,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.84,0:36:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.80,0:36:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I even saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.40,0:36:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I a creep?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.16,0:36:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get scolded,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.00,0:36:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,by the devs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.16,0:36:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Please don't look at things like that!"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.28,0:36:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't draw it in the first place, honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.68,0:36:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll ask me what's wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.44,0:36:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I'm just overflowing with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.68,0:36:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was only the Pre-Training version.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.58,0:36:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at the Post-Training one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.28,0:36:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it went back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.12,0:36:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Post-Training.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.98,0:36:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.20,0:36:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.24,0:36:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That varsity jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.80,0:36:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.40,0:36:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's rare to see her with something like tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.44,0:36:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's apple tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.54,0:36:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.52,0:37:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's drinking that... I didn't know Shiho drank apple tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.72,0:37:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It really gives off that vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.08,0:37:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.96,0:37:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The location looks like it's in front of a music store, which really fits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.60,0:37:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, since Shiho's character color is light green,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.66,0:37:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,using a green apple like this is a great touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.74,0:37:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.69,0:37:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.20,0:37:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost spun around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to spin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.60,0:37:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.16,0:37:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally... Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.38,0:37:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Saki's 2-star card.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.82,0:37:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When Saki wears it, the atmosphere changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.66,0:37:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and she looks so much more mature. It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.56,0:37:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.04,0:38:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The logo on the sleeve is great too. I want that logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.82,0:38:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.76,0:38:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ln logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.86,0:38:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want it so bad, I wish they'd make it into merch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.84,0:38:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone said it's okay to spin as many times as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's embarrassing, so I'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.08,0:38:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You usually do these After Talks alone, at your own pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.60,0:38:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so I end up acting like my usual self, which is embarrassing to watch later.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.88,0:38:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's an official stream, I'm just going at my own pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.96,0:38:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so I start to wonder if this is really okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.19,0:38:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.88,0:38:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.20,0:38:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want that Leo/need logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.24,0:38:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want them to release it as a patch or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.52,0:38:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make it happen someday, higher-ups.
Comment: 0,0:38:47.76,0:38:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.76,0:38:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.98,0:38:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's take a look at the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.72,0:38:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.70,0:39:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, I'd like to talk about the song and the MV while watching the 2D MV for 'Transparent Palette,' which Akuera-san drew specifically for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's watch the 2D MV that was released yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.00,0:42:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.16,0:42:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.60,0:42:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This MV is really great, it has a sense of transparency but it's also poppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.84,0:42:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were recording this song... it's very refreshing, but
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.18,0:42:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the A and B sections, there's a lot of hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.68,0:42:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to convey a sense of bewilderment and not to sing it too strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.86,0:42:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the chorus... how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.02,0:42:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to sing with a sense of transparency, and we all sang it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.16,0:43:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I love the lyric about having apple pie on a day of celebration so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.88,0:43:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the lyrics written for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.32,0:43:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,there haven't been many times where a character's favorite thing is mentioned so directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.92,0:43:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.88,0:43:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it feel like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.24,0:43:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I had that image... I remember it feeling quite fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.96,0:43:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That part just keeps playing in my head. I personally really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.24,0:43:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, I think it was on the Master difficulty chart?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.00,0:43:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,An apple pie appears in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.56,0:43:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They worked hard to make it look like an apple pie, a really big apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.68,0:43:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like, 'Oh, it's an apple pie!' and I played it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.92,0:43:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're curious, please try playing the Master difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.16,0:43:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Shiho's ramen will show up eventually? Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.60,0:43:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Would Shiho even get such a poppy song?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.04,0:44:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd certainly like to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.72,0:44:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Try playing the Master chart.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.50,0:44:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.68,0:44:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Master chart should be available to play right away, so
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.20,0:44:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,please give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.44,0:44:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiho and ramen... I can't quite imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.00,0:44:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A little...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.32,0:44:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they want us to play it that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.20,0:44:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe they want it to be metal?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.66,0:44:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like 'chugga-chugga-chugga-chugga.'
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.88,0:44:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,D-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d-d!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.48,0:44:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Slap bass is impossible... true.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.04,0:44:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The steam from the ramen would be all zigzaggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.28,0:44:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you have a great imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.20,0:45:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In this way, characters' favorite things might be included in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.80,0:45:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.82,0:45:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also happy to see Saki-chan in her outfit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.14,0:45:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I also noticed that the heart marks and logos were different for each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.96,0:45:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very cute 2D MV, so please everyone, check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.68,0:45:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been uploaded to the official Proseka YouTube channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.08,0:45:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.00,0:45:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, our short time is up. This concludes the Proseka After Talk: Unsteady Steady Step edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.24,0:45:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.84,0:45:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It went by so fast, I just realized it's already past 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.80,0:45:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about it when the time passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.06,0:45:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized quite a bit of time had passed while I was talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.36,0:45:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, 'I shouldn't be doing this, I have to watch the MV too,'
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.52,0:45:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.37,0:45:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.56,0:45:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It went by in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.82,0:45:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.14,0:45:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.00,0:45:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just got word...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.68,0:46:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can talk more? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.24,0:46:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, for those who haven't finished the 'Unsteady Steady Step' event story yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.44,0:46:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,even after the next event starts, you can read it all from the Event Story archives,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.00,0:46:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so please give it a read.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.40,0:46:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We are still looking for messages for After Talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.26,0:46:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We're accepting them via the After Talk message channel on the official Proseka Discord or via email.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.02,0:46:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When the next After Talk event is held, please send them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.82,0:46:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please send in messages related to the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.60,0:46:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I had a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.02,0:46:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.12,0:46:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.80,0:46:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.68,0:47:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.60,0:47:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.10,0:47:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I don't know.
